    <mxCell id="ccnote" value="&lt;b&gt;Counter-current&lt;/b&gt;: internal fluid flows in +z, external fluid in &#8722;z.&#10;The jacket inlet at z = L is co-located with the outlet measurement T(L,t)." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#cccccc;fillColor=#f7f7f7;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
